sbe_layout
- Gateway function for layout methods

Description 
 
[xy]=sbe_layout(sbeG,method) 
method: 1 - Random, 2 - Circle, 3 - Tree Ring 
        4 - Kamada-Kawai Spring 
        5 - Gursoy-Atun 
        6 - Fruchterman-Reingold Force Directed
